headline: Gabelli Funds to Host 49th Annual Automotive Symposium at The Encore at Wynn, Las Vegas, Nevada
summary: GREENWICH, Conn., Oct. 28, 2025 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- Gabelli Funds will host its 49th Annual Automotive Symposium on November 3rd and 4th, 2025 at the Encore at Wynn in Las Vegas, Nevada. This two-day symposium will feature presentations by senior management of leading automotive and trucking companies, with a lineup that allows investors to understand the ever-changing dynamics within the automotive industry.
